definitions.definition: Having tooth -like projections on one side, as in a saw .
examples: Many click beetles have serrate antennae.

definitions.definition: Of leaves: having tooth-like projections pointed away from the petiole .

main_definition: Having tooth -like projections on one side, as in a saw .
secondary_definitions: ( botany ) Of leaves: having tooth-like projections pointed away from the petiole .
